      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SASSY SNIPPET (9) comes through a strong form race on debut where she was only 1.6L off the winner at the finish. Three winners have come from six starters since and Pike remains in the saddle. Expect natural progression and she can get the job done his time. DOMINANT FORCE (8) resumed in good order, just missing out in a CL1 event on the Scarpside here 16 days ago. Drawn the inside now with Steve Parnham remaining in the saddle. Fitter and can go one better. TRUE FICTION (2) finished off strongly to just miss over 1000m at Ascot. He should get every chance off the inside for Harvey and he has performed well in stronger races. Can make his presence felt. GUARANTOR (3) can build on the last start win at Northam. MORF (5) comes here without a trial but ended last campaign in hot form. Can return with a bang.",
